flowchart LR
    C([Candidate]) --> R[POST /api/resumes]
    R --> ATS[ATS engine\nscore + verdict + data points]
    ATS --> AIBF[AIBF engine\nbias score + explanation]
    AIBF -->|flagged?| Q{bias_score > upper?}
    Q -- no --> OK[Store: not flagged]
    Q -- yes --> HR[HR review\n/api/admin/flagged]
    HR --> FB[POST /api/admin/feedback\naccept / override]
    FB --> RT[POST /api/model-training/retrain\nrefit + recalibrate threshold]
    RT --> AIBF
